text: Falsamblesthis taeniata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Belon in 1903. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Falsamblesthis taeniata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1903
title: Falsamblesthis taeniata
